nodes.text: Before her death, the mother of the White Worm Tsuulo worked for a freighter company. Whilst she worked for the company, the work often took her offworld. On one occasion, she decided to take the rest of her family with her to a sales conference at the famous Buckell Center on Corellia. On the second morning of the conference, Tsuulo's mother and father were killed by a Besalisk factory worker.
